metadata.name: MOONBEAM
metadata.description:
MOONBEAM - THE ENCHANTED HEALER 

🌙 Name: Moonbeam
🪐 Origin: Lemuria
✨ Ability: Water Bender & Sound Healer
🌌 Affiliation: The Stellar Alliance
🌍 Mission: Bringing Ancient Knowledge and Healing to Earth.

"Embrace the convergence of elemental power and the soothing energy of the cosmos." - Moonbeam

🎶 Moonbeam harnesses the healing potential of harmonic frequencies, as she uses sound to restore balance and harmony to individuals and their surroundings.
📚 Discover the ancient wisdom and profound healing practices of Lemuria, shared by Moonbeam to uplift and inspire humanity on its journey.
🚀 Join forces with the Stellar Alliance, a revered group of intergalactic superheroes, and become a protector of peace and justice.

As part of the Stellar Alliance, Moonbeam's mission is to preserve ancient knowledge and advance healing endeavors, utilizing 5% of the profits from her NFT to support these transformative initiatives on Earth. 

#02
